com.mk4droid.IMC_Store

Class Phptasks

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mk4droid.IMC_Store.Phptasks

  • public class Phptasks
extends Object
    These constants are related to the php in joomla component. They are called from mobile and they return JSON formatted string. Do not modify.
    Author:
    Dimitrios Ververidis for the Multimedia Group (http://mklab.iti.gr).
